name: Cali Comfort Champagne
description:
SPECIALTY BEVERAGE#1

" Our Fine Champagne"

Tasting Notes:

"It's composed of 65% pinot noir & 35% chardonnay, and while the pinot is clearly driving the bus here, the chard shows it's elegant face shiningly. Fruit forward, with the AV pinot bringing creamy strawberry/raspberry, cherry and brambly plum in. The chardonnay component undergoes 100% malolactic fermentation, enhancing the vanilla creaminess. Twenty-first century Cali tropicality brings exotic mango, lychee and pineapple fluff notes. Two years rested on lees, the chard brings a yeasty toastiness, dense with pastry shop butterscotch brioche and lemon chiffon flavors."

Winemaker's Notes:



"This is a beautiful brut, easily worth its price. It shows the fancy elegance of more expensive bubblies, with its refined texture and rich but subtle flavors of strawberries, peaches and brioche." 91 Wine Enthusiast



Sweet this is not, true brut dry-finishing with a crunchy mineral backbone. Our favorite domestic sparkling wine at this price point.


Each state has it's alcohol regulation agency and maintains the right to limit wine shipments entirely or partially. 

WE WILL BE SHIPPING TO THE FOLLOWING STATES VIA UPS:



Arizona (AZ), Alaska (AK), California (CA), Connecticut (CT), Delaware (DE), Florida (FL), Georgia (GA), Hawaii (HI), Iowa (IA), Idaho (ID), Illinois (IL), Indiana (IN), Kansas (KS), Louisiana (LA), Maryland (MD), Michigan (MI), Minnesota (MN), Missouri (MO), North Carolina (NC), North Dakota (ND), Nebraska (NE), New Hampshire (NH), New Jersey (NJ), New Mexico (NM), New York (NY), Ohio (OH), Oregon (OR), Rhode Island (RI), South Carolina (SC), Virginia (VA), Vermont (VT), Wisconsin (WI), Washington (WA), West Virginia (WV), Wyoming (WY).

Wines are shipped by UPS. United States Postal Service does not allow wine shipments, thus we are bound by private carriers. Typically the cost of shipping wines runs approximately $10.00 for single bottle, $12 per double bottle, $13 per four bottle, and $17 per six bottle, and $28 per twelve bottle (case) shipment. Overnight and 2-day expedite orders can be placed online or call in orders for rush ground shipments to 818-305-4492

name: Spacebook Android Tablet Phone!
description:
The next generation of tablets - a mix of Phone and Tablet. With Android 2.2, WiFi, a 7 inch touch screen, front facing camera, 4GB internal memory, AND the ability to make phone calls, the SpaceBook has it all.


The SpaceBook brings a lot of convenience and originality by merging a phone with a tablet. Now, no need for both a smartphone and a tablet any more, because you can do everything directly on the SpaceBook: make and receive calls, write and read SMS and browse the internet using WiFi, watch videos on Dailymotion, read ebooks, send emails, play your favorite games, and much more.

Powered by the ingenious Android 2.2 operating system, the SpaceBook provides true multi-tasking, widgets, and many more features that can't be found anywhere else. It also comes packed with convenient applications such as email, YouTube, Skype, and gives one-touch access to the official Google Marketplace, which is home a huge selection of third-party applications for any purpose - work, personal, or entertainment. Best of all, with the performing Android 2.2, everything works smoothly on this baby! 

At a Glance...

    Android 2.2 Tablet Phone
    Quad-band GSM for phone calls
    7 inch touchscreen
    800MHz processor, 256MB RAM

    4GB internal memory

    Front facing camera
